h's Privacy Policy.</p><p><br></p></div></div><div data-label="Row" id="r-1659377160866" class="gf_row gf_row-gap-0" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1659377160866" data-row-gap="0px" data-extraclass=""><div class="gf_col-md-12 gf_column" id="c-1516320161208" data-id="1516320161208" style="min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Heading" id="e-1659377160865" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-id="1659377160865" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left"><h4 style="text-align: inherit!important;" class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">SUBMITTING YOUR ORDER:</h4></div></div><div data-label="Separator" id="e-1659377160808" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-separator" data-id="1659377160808"><div class="elm gf-elm-left" data-align="left" data-exc=""><hr class="gf_separator"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1659377160795" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-id="1659377160795" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1"><p>An order placed by you in accordance with these Terms of Sale may only be placed through the Site. All orders for Products are subject to acceptance by Turtle Beach. We reserve the right to limit, reject, modify or cancel orders at our sole discretion. Information contained in our advertisements, brochures, other written materials or websites, or information given to you by our agents or employees, constitutes an invitation to bargain only, and does not constitute an offer by us to supply any Product. If we accept your order, we will notify you via email in an order confirmation issued by us to you indicating acceptance of your order (an "Order Confirmation").</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>All orders placed after 2:30pm EST, regardless of shipping option, are processed the next business day (Monday-Friday). We only ship domestically. We cannot ship to a PO box for Ground, Expedited or Priority shipments. We observe all US national holidays.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Before you submit your order please verify that all the information you entered is correct. If you make a mistake entering your email address, your Order Confirmation, which contains valuable purchase information such as your order number and receipt of payment, will be delivered to the incorrect email address. Double check your information before you submit your order.</p><p><br></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" id="r-1659377160830" class="gf_row gf_row-gap-0" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1659377160830" data-row-gap="0px" data-extraclass=""><div class="gf_col-md-12 gf_column" id="c-1516834048204" data-id="1516834048204" style="min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Liquid" id="m-1659377160836" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-liquid" data-id="1659377160836" data-name="Right click on this, and choose Edit Code."><a name="shipping"></a></div><div data-label="Heading" id="e-1659377160894" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-id="1659377160894" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left"><h4 style="text-align: inherit!important;" class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">SHIPPING RATES & INFORMATION:</h4></div></div><div data-label="Separator" id="e-1659377160881" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-separator" data-id="1659377160881"><div class="elm gf-elm-left" data-align="left" data-exc=""><hr class="gf_separator"></div></div><div data-label="Row" id="r-1659377160832" class="gf_row gf_row-gap-0" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1659377160832" data-extraclass="" data-row-gap="0px" style=""><div class="gf_col-md-12 gf_column" id="c-1516834048210" data-id="1516834048210" style="min-height: auto;"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1659377160859" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-id="1659377160859" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-exc=""><p>The shipping choices available from our Site's online store are estimates and do not guarantee the date of delivery. In no event will we be liable for any loss, damage, or penalty resulting from any delay in shipment or delivery. Your package will be processed using the selected shipping method, typically within 1-2 business day of your order being been approved (depending on Product availability and the time of day your order is submitted). All Priority orders are processed at the Signature Required service. After your package has been shipped, you will receive an email containing a shipping confirmation, tracking number and carrier information. In order to avoid any additional return shipping charges, make sure that a household member is there to receive your package. If your Order contains several Products, such Products may be delivered on different days.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Packages returned to our fulfillment centers, due to incorrect addresses will be subject to return shipping fees.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Orders are not processed or shipped on the weekends and holidays. Weekend days should not be considered when calculating your delivery date.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>We do not ship outside of the United States of America and certain of its foreign territories.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>We ask for your patience with tracking updates or potential delivery delays due to increased national shipping volume beyond our control.</p></div></div><div data-label="Row" id="r-1659377160825" class="gf_row gf_row-gap-0" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1659377160825" data-extraclass="" data-row-gap="0px" style=""><div class="gf_col-md-12 gf_column" id="c-1516834048210" data-id="1516834048210" style="min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Liquid" id="m-1659377160860" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-liquid" data-id="1659377160860" data-name="Right click on this, and choose Edit Code."><table class="greyGridTable"><thead><tr><th>SHIPPING METHOD All US Except Puerto Rico</th><th>COST</th><th>ESTIMATED DELIVERY TIME</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>USPS - Parts & Accessories (under 1lb)</td><