g-2">RETURNS/REFUND POLICY & PROCEDURE:  </h4></div></div><div data-label="Separator" id="e-1659377160828" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-separator" data-id="1659377160828" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-left" data-align="left" data-exc=""><hr class="gf_separator"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1659377160810" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-id="1659377160810" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1"><p>Customers who have purchased Products from <a href="https://www.turtlebeach.com" class="">TurtleBeach.com</a> have within 30 days from the time they receive the Product(s) to return the Product(s) for a full refund. Once an order has been placed, it cannot be canceled or modified. Products that were not purchased on TurtleBeach.com are not eligible for return under this policy. Products must be returned in their original condition in their original and undamaged packaging to be eligible for return.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>To request a refund, please send an email to <a href="mailto:sales@turtlebeach.com" class="">sales@turtlebeach.com</a> with your order number in the subject line. A sales representative will advise of your return eligibility and/or any additional action(s) that needs to be taken. You may then be issued a Return Merchandise Authorization ("RMA") number that will be emailed to you with further instructions.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Please ship Products in its original packaging back to Turtle Beach with the RMA number clearly marked on the outside of the shipping carton. Also include the packing slip and a copy of the order in the package. Packages without a valid RMA number may be refused and will be returned at your expense. The RMA expires after 20 days, so please be sure to ship the product within 20 days of receiving your RMA, otherwise it may be refused. Additional Product return instructions may be required.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Turtle Beach will pay for return shipping on all exchanges for damaged/defective product or in cases of our order errors. For all other returns, you are responsible for shipping the product back to us via a traceable method. Original shipping fees are non-refundable. Turtle Beach is not responsible for any returned Products lost or damaged in transit.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>For any order related questions or concerns, please contact Customer Service at <a href="mailto:sales@turtlebeach.com" class="">sales@turtlebeach.com</a>. Please be sure to always reference your order number.</p><p><br></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" id="e-1659377160831" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-id="1659377160831" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center"><h4 style="text-align: left;" class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">CLAIMS FOR DAMAGES:</h4></div></div><div data-label="Separator" id="e-1659377160885" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-separator" data-id="1659377160885"><div class="elm gf-elm-left" data-align="left" data-exc=""><hr class="gf_separator"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1659377160857" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-id="1659377160857" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1"><p>Claims for damages to Products or errors in an Order must be made within 5 days of receipt. Claims for damages must first be reported to the delivering carrier (save all packing and cartons). We are not responsible for any damage to any third-party products connected to our Products.</p></div></div><div data-label="Row" id="r-1659377160910" class="gf_row gf_row-gap-0" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1659377160910" data-row-gap="0px" data-extraclass=""><div class="gf_col-md-12 gf_column" id="c-1516835573212" data-id="1516835573212" style="min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Liquid" id="m-1659377160868" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-liquid" data-id="1659377160868" style="" data-name="Right click on this, and choose Edit Code."><a name="warranty"></a></div><div data-label="Heading" id="e-1659377160841" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-id="1659377160841" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center"><h4 style="text-align: left;" class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">WARRANTY SERVICE:</h4></div></div><div data-label="Separator" id="e-1659377160919" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-separator" data-id="1659377160919"><div class="elm gf-elm-left" data-align="left" data-exc=""><hr class="gf_separator"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1659377160915" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-id="1659377160915" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1"><p>Our warranty refers to the repair or replacement of a defective Product during the warranty period and not a refund. For a description of our warranty policy, please see the warranty policies described on our Site at <a href="https://support.turtlebeach.com/s/article/218942167-Warranty-and-End-User-License?language=en_US" class="" target="_blank">https://support.turtlebeach.com/s/article/218942167-Warranty-and-End-User-License?language=en_US</a>.&nbsp;</p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" id="r-1659377160804" class="gf_row gf_row-gap-0" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1659377160804" data-row-gap="0px" data-extraclass=""><div class="gf_col-md-12 gf_column" id="c-1516835618062" data-id="1516835618062" style="min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Heading" id="e-1659377160909" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-id="1659377160909" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center"><h4 style="text-align: left;" class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">ORDER CONFIRMATION:  </h4></div></div><div data-label="Separator" id="e-1659377160878" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-separator" data-id="1659377160878"><div class="elm gf-elm-left" data-align="left" data-exc=""><hr class="gf_separator"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1659377160943" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-id="1659377160943" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1"><p>Within minutes after your order is submitted, you should receive an Order Confirmation email containing your order number and receipt of payment. You must save this confirmation email for your records.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>If you do not receive an Order Confirmation email, please send an email to <a href="mailto:sales@turtlebeach.com" class="">sales@turtlebeach.com</a> and make sure that you do not have any anti-spamming, filtering or blocking software enabled, as this may prevent you from receiving a reply.</p><p><br></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" id="r-1659377160798" class="gf_row gf_row-gap-0" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1659377160798" data-row-gap="0px" data-extraclass=""><div class="gf_col-md-12 gf_column" id="c-1516835573187" data-id="1516835573187" style="min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Heading" id="e-1659377160867" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-id="1659377160867" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center"><h4 style="text-align: left;" class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">ORDER CHANGES & CANCELLATION:</h4></div></div><div data-label="Separator" id="e-1659377160827" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-separator" data-id="1659377160827"><div class="elm gf-elm-left" data-align="left" data-exc=""><hr class="gf_separator"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1659377160819" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-id="1659377160819" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1"><p>Because of the quick turnaround times with which we ship orders, we cannot change orders after they have been submitted. If you wish to make changes to the delivery destination, you must contact the shipping vendor directly, once you receive a tracking number.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Once an order has been placed, it cannot be canceled or modified unless the Product is unavailable. If you wish to return the Product you are responsible for all additional shipping charges to and from Turtle Beach.</p><p><br></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" id="r-1659377160803" class="gf_row gf_row-gap-0" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1659377160803" data-row-gap="0px" data-extraclass=""><div class="gf_col-md-12 gf_column" id="c-1516835405801" data-id="1516835405801" style="min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Heading" id="e-1659377160877" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-id="1659377160877" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center"><h4 style="text-align: left;" class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">PAYMENTS:  </h4></div></div><div data-label="Separator" id="e-1659377160834" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-separator" data-id="1659377160834"><div class="elm gf-elm-left" data-align="left" data-exc=""><hr class="gf_separator"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1659377160779" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-id="1659377160779" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1"><p>Our online store is hosted on Shopify Inc. (www.shopify.com ). They provide us with the online e-commerce platform and related payment processing services that allow us to sell our products and services to you. We will charge your credit card account upon placement of your order, including all pre-orders placed 30 to 90 days before shipment. By placing an order with us you agree that any credit card and other payment method information provided by you is true and complete and you will pay the applicable listed price(s) in addition to any shipping and handling charges and applicable taxes. We currently accept PayPal, Amazon Pay, Google Pay, Apple Pay and the following credit cards: Mastercard, Visa, Discover and American Express. We reserve the right to modify the accepted payment methods in our discretion and will update the payment methods available on the checkout page. For transact